  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Violence in schools existing, each year about 246 million children suffered from violence or abuse in schools or nearby areas in global level. For lacking of a comprehensive and effective child protection system, especially in schools, children facing risks brought by violence/ abuse, which leads negative effect self-depreciation, aggressive behavior, and unplanned pregnancy etc. The program plans to build and pilot child protection system in 2 schools which is expected to impact 1000 children.</narrative>
